author: Kyle Morris, Kyle Morris
title: Jacksonville Beaches to Reopen with Limitations on Friday
description: Jacksonville, Florida, Mayor Lenny Curry announced Thursday that Jacksonville's beaches will reopen on Friday at 5:00 p.m. for essential activities after being encouraged by positive data regarding COVID-19.
content:
